{"lemma":"جَلَداتُ","slug":"جَلَداتُ","root":"ج.ل.د","root_slug":"ج-ل-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ل-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَلْدَة","root":"جلد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6101","n6110","n6111","n6112"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of جَلَدَ (jalada): a lash","examples":[{"text":"اَلزَّانِيَةُ وَٱلزَّانِي فَٱجْلِدُوا كُلَّ وَاحِدٍ مِنْهُمَا مِئَةَ جَلْدَةٍ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a piece of skin"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6101","headword_ar":"جَلَدَهُ","root":"jld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalodN","text_ar":"جَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt, his skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) like as you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^asahu","text_ar":"رَاَسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baTanahu","text_ar":"بَطَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he beat his skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he beat him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a criminal: (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he struck him"},{"kind":"text","text":"with a whip, and with a sword: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he flogged him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a whip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with whips:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladotu","text_ar":"جَلَدْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes written and pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalad~u","text_ar":"جَلَدُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF on the letter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladahu AlHad~a","text_ar":"جَلَدَهُ الحَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inflicted upon him the flogging ordained by the law."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladati AlHay~apu","text_ar":"جَلَدَتِ الحَيَّةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The serpent bit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, accord. to some, one says of the serpent called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowadu","text_ar":"اَسْوَدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", specially,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajolidu bi*anabihi","text_ar":"يَجْلِدُ بِذَنَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it strikes with its tail"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalada jaAriyatahu","text_ar":"جَلَدَ جَارِيَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lay with his young woman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female slave."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalada Eumayorapa","text_ar":"جَلَدَ عُمَيْرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakaHa Alyada","text_ar":"نَكَحَ اليَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], a metonymical phrase:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalodu Eumayorapa","text_ar":"جَلْدُ عُمَيْرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaDoxaDapu","text_ar":"الخَضْخَضَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotimonaA='u biAlyadi","text_ar":"الاِسْتِمْنَا=ءُ بِاليَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~adoliylu","text_ar":"التَّدْلِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAiEotimaAru","text_ar":"الاِعْتِمَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the similar act of a woman is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_iloTaAfu","text_ar":"الاـِلْطَافُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 572.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalada bihi AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"جَلَدَ بِهِ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smote the ground with him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he threw him down prostrate on the ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julida bihi","text_ar":"جُلِدَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fell down"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground by reason of much sleepiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julida bihi nuwomFA","text_ar":"جُلِدَ بِهِ نُوْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotu A^ata$ad~adu fayujoladu biY","text_ar":"كُنْتُ اَتَشَدَّدُ فَيُجْلَدُ بِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a trad., means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I used to exert my strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"energy, but"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleep would overcome me so that I fell down."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladahu EalaY AlA^amori","text_ar":"جَلَدَهُ عَلَى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He compelled him against his will to do the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yujoladu bikul~i xayorK","text_ar":"يُجْلَدُ بِكُلِّ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or, as related by AHát,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yjl*","text_ar":"يجلذ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*","text_ar":"ذ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is imagined to possess every good quality."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) But the saying of EshSháfi'ee"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna mujaAlidN yujoladu","text_ar":"كَانَ مُجَالِدٌ يُجْلَدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mujálid used to be pronounced a liar,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspected and accused of lying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julidati","text_ar":"جُلِدَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, Msb,) the verb being in the pass. form, (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalidat","text_ar":"جَلِدَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) a verb of the same form as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [or both may be correct, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Duribat","text_ar":"ضُرِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daribat","text_ar":"ضَرِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the same sense;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoladat","text_ar":"اَجْلَدَت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [but this last I believe to be a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ujolidat","text_ar":"اُجْلِدَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uDoribat","text_ar":"اُضْرِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smitten, by hoar-frost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rime."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jld Albaqolu","text_ar":"جلد البَقْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalida","text_ar":"جَلِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The herbs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leguminous plants, were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smitten, thereby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ujoliduwA","text_ar":"اُجْلِدُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"(men)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smitten, thereby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaluda","text_ar":"جَلُدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaAdapN","text_ar":"جَلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juluwdapN","text_ar":"جُلُودَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladN","text_ar":"جَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or this last is a simple subst., L) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoluwdN","text_ar":"مَجْلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (an inf. n. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoluwfN","text_ar":"مَحْلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoquwlN","text_ar":"مَعْقُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajal~ada","text_ar":"تَجَلَّدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Esr","text_ar":"عسر"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hardy, strong, sturdy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * L, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and enduring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"patient."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","Mgh","TA","A","L"]},{"entry_id":"n6110","headword_ar":"جَلْدَةٌ","root":"jld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladN","text_ar":"جَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6111","headword_ar":"جِلْدَةٌ","root":"jld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a more particular term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilodN","text_ar":"جِلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L;) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of skin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-  One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilodapu AlEayoni","text_ar":"جِلْدَةُ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eyelid"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN mino jilodatinaA","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ مِنْ جِلْدَتِنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men, of ourselves,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of our kinsfolk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalodN","text_ar":"جَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6112","headword_ar":"جَلَدَةٌ","root":"jld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaladN","text_ar":"جَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}